But I will pay for everything.

525
00:28:10,167 --> 00:28:11,900
So that one day,

526
00:28:12,767 --> 00:28:17,133
I may be worthy of your love

527
00:28:17,267 --> 00:28:19,033
and forgiveness.

528
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:27,533
[EMOTIONAL MUSIC PLAYING]

529
00:28:34,033 --> 00:28:37,433
Pa, the syndicate you fought
your whole life to destroy

530
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:39,167
has finally fallen.

531
00:28:40,633 --> 00:28:44,567
They'll never prey
on anyone again.

532
00:28:44,667 --> 00:28:46,100
It took a while,

533
00:28:46,267 --> 00:28:52,500
but I finally got justice
for you, Pa.

534
00:28:53,967 --> 00:28:58,067
Everything you and Col. Enrico
sacrificed weren't wasted.

535
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:02,633
I love you so much, Pa.

536
00:29:02,733 --> 00:29:09,167
